00:16:28,519 --> 00:16:29,679
Tuan Yun.

249
00:16:33,120 --> 00:16:35,820
Tentu saja. Kamu pasti bisa.

250
00:16:41,129 --> 00:16:44,970
Jadi, mereka berdua orang yang sama?

